OL,1,MA]G  Wigan and Xenograd Twinning   Px}0
OL,2,                       k                
OL,3,                                  Q "###
OL,4,C The Orakle AI has decreed a formal    
OL,5,C union between the Great District of   
OL,6,GCWigan and our industrial citadel      
OL,7,C Xenograd.                             
OL,8,C                                       
OL,9,  SHARED OBJECTIVES:F                   
OL,10,C 1) Exchange of coal extraction tech.  
OL,11,C 2) Standardisation of crust ratios.  F
OL,12,C 3) Joint SABRE patrols at the pier.   
OL,14,F Citizens of Xenograd are encouraged to
OL,15,FFadopt a "Wigan Peer" (a designated    
OL,16,FFBritish worker) for monitoring.       
OL,17,F                                       
OL,18,  COMMEMORATIVE RATION UPDATE:FTo       
OL,19,F celebrate, all Xenoxxx Pie-Depots will
OL,20,F issue a limited "Goujon/Potato"       
OL,21,F pastry. Pay-by-Palm required.         
OL,22,FM"Glory to the twins. Data is Unity"   
OL,23,C                            More--->1/2
OL,24,ANext  BDuties   CReporting   FPurity   
